    "narrative": {
        "setting": "Post-collapse industrial zone overrun by automated defense systems.",
        "conflict": "Machines defend the refinery against all intruders. Humans are no longer expected.",
        "win_state": "Survive the escape timer and exit the complex after planting detonators.",
        "fail_state": "Detected and killed or time expires.",
        "main_character": "Jake Jackson was 10 years old when his family was killed. The incident happened at the final stages of the \"Drone Wars\". This uprising of AI and robotics technology was the culimination of decades of adotption of automation. Every device that could be \"AI enhanced\" was mandated to be upgraded by law. This included everything from the microwave oven to the surface street transportation of all kinds. All planes,trains and automobiles were given AI networked automation. Jake was taken in by a family of the resistance culture and trained in the ways of kinetic and technological warfare against machines. ",
        "story": "After the Drone Wars, pockets of human resistance remained but lived mainly underground.There are rumors of oaises of humanity still surviving above ground, but they are few and far between.Most activity in the resistance takes place via 'technological asassins'. These asassins are part of a vast and mysterious network of freedom fighters."
    },
